When first downloaded open all excel files one, disabled protected mode(in the prompt) for all the files
Go to file
Go to options
Go to formulas
Check enable iterative calculations box
Set maximum iterations to 10
Close the files
After closing, open them all again
You can now play
Game is played in the Game file, but all other files must be open in order for it to work
Type start in the input box to start,
Type restart to restart(full restart!)
